<concept id="concept_w2l_g22_xdb">
    <title>Fax to Email</title>
    <shortdesc>Fax to Email feature helps you receive faxes on your smart phone or computer. Yeastar
            <ph product="s-series">S-Series VoIP PBX</ph><ph product="cloudpbx">Cloud PBX</ph> will
        convert the received fax and forward it to an extension user's email.</shortdesc>
