    <conbody>
        <section id="section_apx_t22_xdb">
            <title>Steps to Configure 'Fax to Email'</title>
            <p>
                <ol id="ol_wjr_cf2_xdb">
                    <li>Configure the PBX <uicontrol>System Email</uicontrol>.<p>Make sure the PBX
                            system email works, or the PBX cannot forward the received faxes to an
                            extension user's email.</p></li>
                    <li>Check if the extension user's email is configured.<p><image
                                href="../Images/admin/extension_email.png" id="image_lxw_qf2_xdb"
                                width="650"/></p></li>
                    <li>Configure the destination of your inbound route.<p>
                            <ul id="ul_cz1_wf2_xdb">
                                <li>If you want to<xref
                                        href="receive_fax_via_fax_detection.dita#task_yzr_n12_xdb">
                                        receive fax via fax detection</xref>, set the
                                        <uicontrol>Destination</uicontrol> to <codeph>IVR</codeph>,
                                    and set <uicontrol>Fax Destination</uicontrol> to <codeph>Fax to
                                        Email</codeph>.<p><image
                                            href="../Images/admin/fax_to_email_fax_detection.png"
                                            id="image_qhg_sg2_xdb" width="650"/></p></li>
                                <li>If you want to <xref
                                        href="receive_fax_through_a_dedicated_trunk.dita#task_y3m_kxd_xdb"
                                        >receive fax through a private trunk</xref>, set the
                                        <uicontrol>Destination</uicontrol> to <codeph>Fax to
                                        Email</codeph>.<p><image
                                            href="../Images/admin/fax_to_email_destination.png"
                                            id="image_rkf_tg2_xdb" width="650"/></p></li>
                            </ul>
                        </p></li>
                </ol>
            </p>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
